data.description: This 4bdr, 2-1/2bth is more than just a house it’s a home where memories were made, dreams realized. Convenience at the forefront, ensuring open concept living. Dining or private study with half bath on main level perfect for guests, while a well appointed full bath upstairs caters to needs of rest of family. Enjoy the abundant windows and impressive 18 foot ceilings in family room. Your primary suite is a true retreat, boasting spa-like ensuite bath, separate shower, and walk-in closet creating a serene oasis to unwind after a long day. Upstairs you'll find a game room and 3 generously sized bedrooms providing comfort and privacy. Outside, the cul-de-sac location offers a peaceful setting with an expansive backyard providing ample space for gardening, relaxation, or creating your own private sanctuary. Don't miss the golden opportunity to infuse this home with your personal style and TLC. Schedule a showing and envision the exciting possibilities that await your decorative touch.
